{"tid":1685901,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚大胃王！曼谷「最巨型漢堡」 重13磅 吃完獎你1萬泰銖","createTime":"2019-10-31T23:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T22:11:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"256bc038e1aa32b24c2075eeb682bda6a9b4639b","tid":1685901,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:20:39.000Z","msg":"自問「食力」驚人的人士注意！泰國曼谷漢堡店Chris Steaks and Burgers推出號稱「最巨型漢堡」，挑戰大胃王，只要你在九分鐘內吃完，就可拿到1萬泰銖（2,595港元）獎金，吸引不少YouTuber前來挑戰。<br />\n這個漢堡包足足重13磅，有巨型肉餅、煙肉、炸洋蔥圈和蛋黃醬，熱量高達1萬千卡路里。漢堡店東主科姆德希（Komdech Kongsuwan）聲稱這是全泰國最巨型的漢堡，某次他見到有三名食客一起吃掉此漢堡後，想出挑戰大胃王的比賽作招徠。目前每天都有新的挑戰者來到嘗試，但不是每個人都能夠在限時內完成。<br />\n挑戰失敗的食客包括巴空（Pakorn Porncheewangkoon），他似乎對漢堡有點怕怕了：「我以後還會吃漢堡，但最近應該不會了。」這個巨型漢堡牛肉版售2,500泰銖（649港元），豬肉版則售3,500泰銖（908港元）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191031/large/1572493773_cceb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191031%2Flarge%2F1572493773_cceb.jpg&h=509326a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191101/60214466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F60214466&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5c29b40e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F60214466&h=e485f13c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191101/60214466</a>"},{"pid":"76d04f6c5d183010bc06484ae6d955319a8ad4f4","tid":1685901,"uid":280493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRfwDu9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRfwDu9.gif&h=0468d78e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"393e640128f8e460612df259330b479e4496866f","tid":1685901,